{"tid":361110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一場意外，搞掂兩件社會渣滓","createTime":"2017-08-15T23:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T02:31:58.000Z","uid":28831,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c8ace27b1b651b67497eee2d0d9d0a10124b97","tid":361110,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"64歲的士司機，涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人死亡被捕<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴漆咸道南發生奪命車禍。昨深夜約11時50分，一輛私家車沿漆咸道南慢線往海傍方向行駛，至尖東海濱平台對開，司機發現快線有一名男子倒臥地上，立即在距離男子約20米停車及打著死火燈。<br />\n同時間一輛空載的士沿快線駛至，司機未有察覺將男子輾過，駛前約30米始停下。男子身體受傷大量出血。救護員到場搶救，送院證實死亡。據稱，的士輾過路中物體，司機停車查看時，赫然發覺是一名男子。64歲姓鄭的士司機涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人死亡被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n警方初步調查，死者是一名南亞男子，年約40歲，身高約1.68米，瘦身材，蓄啡短髮，事發時身穿灰色短袖上衣、藍白色長褲及及啡色拖鞋。<br />\n<br />\n口德村村民全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0499bf951edb0c60e7db4a018c682198aa6fc06f","tid":361110,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T23:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deaa306e566b49005ee301bd173ce7b4f88218f","tid":361110,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T23:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86583ec572d8b5a1e498425a510506d51e37f81","tid":361110,"uid":53429,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:17:14.000Z","msg":"口德邨居民仲未進場"},{"pid":"1a9cf607d0c67c4796d0ea808e3f4acac2fc662a","tid":361110,"uid":40932,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>口德邨居民仲未進場</blockquote><br />\n口德村d人睇係咪女渣"},{"pid":"eb1a216cc95c13bdcc3aa64939d14e74f1d48c35","tid":361110,"uid":124458,"like":1,"dislike":6,"scor